704079f-a.folder: Elderts Lane & Glenmore Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
704079f-a.text:
Elderts Lane, in line of Glenmore Ave., showing the John Drew house formerly at Old South Road and Elderts Lane. Eugene L. Ambruster
states that this house was moved to the city line.

Date ?

Eugene L. Ambruster Collection.

704080f-a.folder: Elderts Lane & Glenmore Avenue, Brooklyn, NY
704080f-a.text:
566-570 Elderts Lane, west side, between Glenmore and Pitkin Aves., showing in the foreground the home of "Old John Drew", from 186O-1873. This house formerly stood one block east of its present location at a point where
Old South Road met New Lots Road at Elderts Lane.

About 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
